msgctxt "an9.22:6.5"
msgid "Idamassa vaṇṇasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re beautiful, I say. "

msgctxt "an9.22:6.6"
msgid "Lābhī kho pana hoti cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ. "
