msgstr "These are the three wild people. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an9.22:7.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo assaparassā? "
msgstr "And what are the three excellent horses? "

msgctxt "an9.22:7.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco assaparasso … pe … "
msgstr "One excellent horse … "

msgctxt "an9.22:7.3"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca. "
msgstr "is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned. "

msgctxt "an9.22:7.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo assaparassā. "
msgstr "These are the three excellent horses. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an9.22:8.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo purisaparassā? "
msgstr "What are the three excellent people? "

msgctxt "an9.22:8.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco purisaparasso … pe … "
msgstr "One excellent person … "

msgctxt "an9.22:8.3"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca. "
msgstr "is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an9.22:9.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, purisaparasso … pe … "
msgstr "And how is an excellent person … "

msgctxt "an9.22:9.2"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca? "
msgstr "fast, beautiful, and well proportioned? "

msgctxt "an9.22:9.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā opapātiko hoti, tattha parinibbāyī anāvattidhammo tasmā lokā. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant, with the ending of the five lower fetters, is reborn spontaneously. They’re extinguished there, and are not liable to return from that world. "

msgctxt "an9.22:9.4"
msgid "Idamassa javasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re fast, I say. "

msgctxt "an9.22:9.5"
msgid "Abhidhamme kho pana abhivinaye pañhaṃ puṭṭho vissajjeti, no saṃsādeti. "
msgstr "When asked a question about the teaching or training, they answer without faltering. "

msgctxt "an9.22:9.6"
msgid "Idamassa vaṇṇasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re beautiful, I say. "

msgctxt "an9.22:9.7"
msgid "Lābhī kho pana hoti cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ. "
msgstr "They receive robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick. "

msgctxt "an9.22:9.8"
msgid "Idamassa ārohapariṇāhasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re well proportioned, I say. "

msgctxt "an9.22:9.9"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, purisaparasso javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca. "
msgstr "This is how an excellent person fast, beautiful, and well proportioned. "

msgctxt "an9.22:9.10"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo purisaparassā. "
msgstr "These are the three excellent people. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.400, sc10
msgctxt "an9.22:10.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo bhaddā assājānīyā? "
msgstr "And what are the three fine thoroughbred horses? "

msgctxt "an9.22:10.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco bhaddo assājānīyo … pe … "
msgstr "One fine thoroughbred horse … "

msgctxt "an9.22:10.3"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca. "
msgstr "is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned. "

msgctxt "an9.22:10.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo bhaddā assājānīyā. "
msgstr "These are the three fine thoroughbred horses. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an9.22:11.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo bhaddā purisājānīyā? "
msgstr "And what are the three fine thoroughbred people? "

msgctxt "an9.22:11.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco bhaddo purisājānīyo … pe … "
msgstr "One fine thoroughbred person … "

msgctxt "an9.22:11.3"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca. "
msgstr "is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "an9.22:12.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhaddo purisājānīyo … pe … "
msgstr "And how is a fine thoroughbred person … "

msgctxt "an9.22:12.2"
msgid "javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca? "
msgstr "fast, beautiful, and well proportioned? "

msgctxt "an9.22:12.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "It’s a mendicant who realizes the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due to the ending of defilements. "

msgctxt "an9.22:12.4"
msgid "Idamassa javasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re fast, I say. "

msgctxt "an9.22:12.5"
msgid "Abhidhamme kho pana abhivinaye pañhaṃ puṭṭho vissajjeti, no saṃsādeti. "
msgstr "When asked a question about the teaching or training, they answer without faltering. "

msgctxt "an9.22:12.6"
msgid "Idamassa vaṇṇasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re beautiful, I say. "

msgctxt "an9.22:12.7"
msgid "Lābhī kho pana hoti cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ. "
msgstr "They receive robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick. "

msgctxt "an9.22:12.8"
msgid "Idamassa ārohapariṇāhasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re well proportioned, I say. "

msgctxt "an9.22:12.9"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhaddo purisājānīyo javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca. "
msgstr "This is how a fine thoroughbred person is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned. "

msgctxt "an9.22:12.10"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo bhaddā purisājānīyā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the three fine thoroughbred people.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.22:12.11"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

